description:
This is a 356 minute workout called 'Best Running Playlist Ever' from the channel Carrie Spaniol.
The workout falls under Cardio/Running and Cardio/Treadmill.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Nightclub Workout and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The The Nightclub Workout vibe means Lights down, music up, full-body euphoria. This is especially good for When you want to move like no one’s watching and feel amazing. The The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe means Beat-driven, strong but fluid, music-infused. This is especially good for When you want strength and rhythm to blend seamlessly..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.
